hey realized the capabilities we have to develop a track bike due to our in-house mold making and carbon frame manufacturing set up.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pendred\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"a few project\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"the run\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"a few factory visits\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"the capabilities\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"a track bike\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"house\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon frame manufacturing\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We initially started working with them to prototype the wide fork/stay design that British Cycling had as a plan B project that would be used in Paris.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}, {\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6565389123414896e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wide fork\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1887}, {\"n