l, managing director with Hope Technology says, \\\"the in\\u2010house team has unrivaled engineering expertise with 30 years of composite experience and two Olympics behind them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jay_Weatherill\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.482889481351686e-12, \"text\": \"Weatherill\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jay_Weatherill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jay_Weatherill\"}, {\"begin\": 2424, \"end\": 2439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope_Technology\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hope Technology\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope_Technology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope_Technology\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hope\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"the manufacturing\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"managing director\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"the in\\u2010house team\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"engineering expertise\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"30 years\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"composite experience\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"two Olympics\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British car brand Lotus meanwhile handles the \\\"front forks and handlebars for the new bike, working with Hope to integrate these components into the overall package.\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2571, \"end\": 2578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999770575416, \"rank\": 2.2540056260819848e-08, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.or