tence\": \"Like the Look P24, it is wide and split but it differs in that it comes back together before joining the rest of the frame.\", \"from\": 5535, \"to\": 5658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Look P24\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5552}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 5636, \"to\": 5644}, {\"ngram\": \"the frame\", \"from\": 5648, \"to\": 5657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's reminiscent of the Trek IsoFlow design which Trek shared helps speed up the air between the rider's legs.\", \"from\": 5659, \"to\": 5769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Trek IsoFlow design\", \"from\": 5679, \"to\": 5702}, {\"ngram\": \"Trek\", \"from\": 5709, \"to\": 5713}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5743}, {\"ngram\": \"the rider's legs\", \"from\": 5752, \"to\": 5768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not in quite the same location though and Hope did not share specifics on the reasons for any of the design details.\", \"from\": 5770, \"to\": 5891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5817, \"end\": 5821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\", \"score\": 0.9999999895517249, \"rank\": 1.0448095803846475e-08, \"text\": \"Hope\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite the same location\", \"from\": 5782, \"to\": 5805}, {\"ngram\": \"specifics\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 5845}, {\"ngram\": \"the reasons\", \"from\": 5849, \"to\": 5860}, {\"ngram\": \"the design details\", \"from\": 5872, \"to\": 5890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with the updated aero, Renishaw had a bit of a chance to highlight the brand's additive manufacturing expertise as well.\", \"from\": 5893, \"to\": 6019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5922, \"end\": 5930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renishaw_plc\", \"score\": 0.999999768899242, \"rank\": 2.3110063800414152e-07, \"text\": \"Renishaw\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"]