 8074, \"to\": 8082}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a325,000 + VAT\", \"from\": 8089, \"to\": 8102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then if you want the Standard Lotus 3D printed fork that's an additional \\u00a32000 + VAT.\", \"from\": 8104, \"to\": 8189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Standard Lotus 3D\", \"from\": 8121, \"to\": 8142}, {\"ngram\": \"fork\", \"from\": 8151, \"to\": 8155}, {\"ngram\": \"VAT\", \"from\": 8185, \"to\": 8188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to also add the Twin Seat Post that's another \\u00a32,000 + VAT.\", \"from\": 8190, \"to\": 8261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Twin Seat Post\", \"from\": 8214, \"to\": 8232}, {\"ngram\": \"another \\u00a32,000 + VAT\", \"from\": 8240, \"to\": 8260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add all that up and you still need wheels and your options are Disc Rear (\\u00a32,700.00 inc vat), Disc Front (\\u00a32,500.00 inc vat), Trispoke Front (\\u00a32,700.00 inc vat), Hope HR Disc Rear (\\u00a34,200.00 inc vat), and Hope HR Disc Front (\\u00a34,000.00 inc vat).\", \"from\": 8262, \"to\": 8506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8424, \"end\": 8428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\", \"score\": 0.9999999895517249, \"rank\": 1.0448095803846475e-08, \"text\": \"Hope\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\"}, {\"begin\": 8467, \"end\": 8471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\", \"score\": 0.9999999895517249, \"rank\": 1.0448095803846475e-08, \"text\": \"Hope\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wheels\", \"from\": 8297, \"to\": 8303}, {\"ngram\": \"your options\", \"from\": 8308, \"to\": 8320}, {\"ngram\": \"Disc Rear\", \"from\": 8325, \"to\": 8334}, {\"ngram\": \"(\\u00a32,700.00 inc vat\", \"from\": 8335, \"to\": 8353}, {\"ngram\": \"Disc Front\", \"from\": 8356, \"to\": 8366}, {\"ngram\":